# We validate:
#   FE  via fixest::feols(y ~ x1 + x2 | i, ...) + sandwich vcovHC HC0/HC1
#   FD  via lm on first differences within each entity + sandwich HC0/HC1
#
# Tolerance target downstream: 6 decimal places on coefficients, 4 on SE.
